#### BUG-06: Password Disimpan Plaintext

**Lokasi:** [AuthController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/pustakanusates/pustakanusa-backend/app/Http/Controllers/Api/AuthController.php#L28) + [User.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/pustakanusates/pustakanusa-backend/app/Models/User.php#L49)

**Problem:**
- `AuthController::login()` membandingkan password langsung: `->where('password', $request->password)` — tanpa `Hash::check()`
- `User` model: komentar `❌ password hashing DIHAPUS` pada casts — password tidak di-hash saat disimpan
- `UserController::store()` menyimpan password raw: `'password' => $request->password ?? '123456'`

Ini adalah **kerentanan keamanan kritis**. Password semua user terekspos dalam plaintext.

