#### BUG-17: `storage:link` Mungkin Belum Dijalankan

**Problem:** File upload disimpan ke disk `public` (`storage/app/public/ebooks/...`), dan frontend mengakses via `http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/...`. Namun `.env` menunjukkan `FILESYSTEM_DISK=local` (default). Jika `php artisan storage:link` belum dijalankan, symlink `public/storage → storage/app/public` belum ada, sehingga semua uploaded file (PDF & cover) **tidak bisa diakses** dari browser.

**Fix:** Jalankan `php artisan storage:link`.

